I have always used Hafler DH-500's for all my live audio needs and love them
to death.  I have been looking at the Hafler P7000 amps and was wondering if
anyone has any feedback on them that they would like to share.  They will be
used to power my Cerwin Vega speakers models B-36A subs, V-37D tops and G-15
tops.
